l/medium websites,\n                            landing pages, online resumes and portfolios. 2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and\n                            themes help you to start easily.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"item mbr-flex\" mbr-class=\"{'last': steps == 1}\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\">\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"step-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">4</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-box\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText || showCardsubTitle\">\n                        <h4 class=\"icon-subtitle card-title mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".icon-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardsubTitle\"><b>Modelos de salud en el mundo</b></h4>\n\n                        <h4 class=\"icon-title card-title mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".icon-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Smart Home Security</b></h4>\n                        <h5 class=\"icon-text mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".icon-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\">Tendrás la oportunidad de comparar el sistema colombiano con otros modelos de salud que existen en el mundo. Esto te permitirá ver distintas formas de organizar la atención en salud y reflexionar sobre sus ventajas y desafíos.</h5>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item mbr-flex\" mbr-if=\"steps > 1\" mbr-class=\"{'last': steps == 2}\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\">\n                        <span class=\"step-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">2</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-box\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText || showCardsubTitle\">\n          